                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>thren in <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName>. Excuse the trifle: the french<lb/> say:\n                “On fait ce qu'on peut, et non pas ce qu'on<lb/> vent” If this trifling amount must\n                appear in your<lb/> Occident, please not to mention my name in no shape<lb/> nor\n                form—only say: received from <persName>Rosalta</persName> and<lb/> nothing more.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Receive my very best wishes, and believe me,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Dear sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">Yours, Respectfully,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">A. Myerston</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
